Suggests: update-motd
Description: Update notification system for Distiller by Pamir-AI
 Automated APT update checker with systemd integration for Distiller
 edge devices.
 .
 Features:
  - Automatic detection of available package updates
  - System integration via systemd timer (daily checks)
  - MOTD (Message of the Day) notifications for SSH sessions
  - D-Bus notification support for desktop environments
  - LED status indicators (blue fade during update, green fade on success)
  - CLI for manual update checking and package management
  - Configurable update policies and notification preferences
 .
 This package provides a user-friendly way to stay informed about system updates
 on embedded Distiller devices running Debian/Ubuntu-based distributions.
